<title>USA: Sterling Commerce offering priced at $29/shr.</title>
<headline>Sterling Commerce offering priced at $29/shr.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-02-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sterling Commerce Inc Tuesday said its public offering of 12.5 million shares of its common stock were priced at $29 per share.</p>
<p>Alex Brown &amp; Sons Inc and Goldman, Sachs &amp; Co are the managing underwriters for the offering. Sterling Commerce said it has granted the underwriters an over-allotment option to purchase up to an additional 1.875 million shares of stock at the public offering price.</p>
</text>
